reviewText: The one thing that caught my eye is all of the girls are red heads. Many different shades of red. That was really the only special thing about this movie.

Unless you just want to watch a few semi good looking solo women doing the same thing for almost 2 hrs who are closer to 30 yrs old than 20 don't buy this DVD. Very boring after 15 minuets. Peep Show Uncensored Vintage Erotica!
